room_title: Escape room "Alien Escape" by Green Light Escape Room in Wilmington
review: We had a great time playing Alien Escape and loved the room. The game play was awesome with some pretty cool elements. Our Game Master was friendly and very helpful. The owners were awesome and have done a great job with their rooms. We can't wait to play more!

room_title: Escape room "Alien Escape" by Green Light Escape Room in Wilmington
review: We had the best time ever! The Alien room was challenging and very well designed. We will definitely be back to try the other rooms!

room_title: Escape room "Alien Escape" by Green Light Escape Room in Wilmington
review: My wife and I wanted to try a room and decided to go with the alien abduction. It was nothing short of impressive. The puzzles within a puzzle, distractors, and just overall challenge was something we enjoyed very much. We were the only two in the room and still had a blast and completed it. Highly recommend!
